// Page HeroOrVigilante Text :
"P1591279698" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Cracked Cell Phone</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find a mostly intact cell phone.  On it, you find some startling information.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>On the cracked cell phone you discover a ransom note that was sent via text message to the Paragon City authorities.  The demands are being made by an Arachnos Operative who is holding a group of British foreign diplomats hostage and is threatening to kill them if their demands aren't met by midnight tonight.<br><br></scale></color></font>You could rescue the diplomats.  By doing so you might allow the Arachnos Operative to escape, but at least the foreign diplomats will be safe.<br><br> Alternatively, you could stop this threat here and now and show Arachnos that the heroes of Paragon City don't cooperate with terrorists.  This might put the diplomats' lives in jeopardy, but at least the Operative won't get a chance to take hostages again."
// Answer Text :
"P1330390896" "HERO: Rescue the foreign diplomats from the Arachnos terrorists."
// Answer Text :
"P448030826" "VIGILANTE: Ignore the hostages and take down the Arachnos Operative."
// Page Rogue Text :
"P859603818" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Cracked Cell Phone</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find a mostly intact cell phone. On it, you find some startling information.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>On the cracked cell phone you discover a ransom note that was sent via text message to the Paragon City authorities.  The demands are being made by an Arachnos Operative who is holding a group of British foreign diplomats hostage and is threatening to kill them if their demands aren't met by midnight tonight.<br><br></scale></color></font>Rescuing these hapless diplomats sounds like the right thing to do.  Besides, sticking it to Arachnos is always fun."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
"P1342464925" "Now is not a good time to investigate this tip.  Wait until you are within the streets of Paragon City before you attempt any investigation."
// Answer Text :
"P385518726" "Investigate this tip later"
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


