// Page HeroOrVigilante Text :
"P3869915790" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>An Obvious Trap</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You very conveniently overhear a Nemesis communique that piques your interest.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>A high ranking Nemesis soldier - or perhaps even Lord Nemesis himself - barks threats over the Paragon City emergency broadcast system, threatening to blow up a nearby office building unless his demands are met.</scale></color></font><br><br>Fully aware that this could be a trap, you could hurry to that office building and diffuse the bombs before they harm any citizens.<br><br>Alternatively you could chance that this is just a decoy and go after where the communique originated from and get a drop on the broadcaster."
// Answer Text :
"P1571320395" "HERO: Diffuse the bomb threat!"
// Answer Text :
"P786900115" "VIGILANTE: Go after the broadcaster of the bomb threat!"
// Page Rogue Text :
"P2387053161" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>An Obvious Trap</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You very conveniently overhear a Nemesis communique that piques your interest.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>A high ranking Nemesis soldier - or perhaps even Lord Nemesis himself - barks threats over the Paragon City emergency broadcast system, threatening to blow up a nearby office building unless his demands are met.</scale></color></font><br><br>This seems like an obvious trap, but you could check it out and make sure no one gets hurt.  There are bombs to disarm and likely Nemesis soldiers waiting for you."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


