// Page HeroOrVigilante Text :
"P180479643" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Desperate Cry For Help</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You nearly trip over a half dead man who begs for your help.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>The man feebily grabs your ankle and in a raspy and exhausted voice says:</scale></color></font><br><br><color orange>'{HeroName}?  Is that you?  Help us, help all of us.  Crey has been pulling people off of the streets and using them for experiments.  I barely managed to escape.  They were awful.  They tortured us.  Loaded us full of chemicals and exposed us to things that no human should ever experience.  Help them, please!  Some are in worse shape than I am, they're dying {HeroName}!  Dying!</color><br><br>There's a chance that those citizens are still alive, you could break into that lab and liberate them.<br><br>Alternatively you could avenge those poor hapless citizens and bring the fight to Crey by destroying one of their key labs in Crey's Folly!"
// Answer Text :
"P74778227" "HERO: Rescue the citizens before it's too late."
// Answer Text :
"P2578192314" "VIGILANTE: Blow up an important Crey laboratory."
// Page Rogue Text :
"P139580298" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Desperate Cry For Help</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You nearly trip over a half dead man who begs for your help.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>The man feebily grabs your ankle and in a raspy and exhausted voice says:</scale></color></font><br><br><color orange>'{HeroName}?  Is that you?  Help us, help all of us.  Crey has been pulling people off of the streets and using them for experiments.  I barely managed to escape.  They were awful.  They tortured us.  Loaded us full of chemicals and exposed us to things that no human should ever experience.  Help them, please!  Some are in worse shape than I am, they're dying {HeroName}!  Dying!</color><br><br>No one deserves the fate that has been forced upon these people, you shudder at the thought of what they must have experienced."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


