"P2947877323" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Wanted Poster With Your Face</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>While going about your business your gaze falls upon a Longbow wanted poster with your name and face on it.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>You pull the poster from its posted location and read it carefully</scale></color></font><br><br><color orange><scale 1.5><span align=center>LONGBOW WANTED FUGITIVE</scale><br><br>ATTEMPTED MURDER, ARMED ROBBERY<br><br></color></span>Below this is a pair of pictures of you.  The first is a headshot of yourself used in your Paragon City hero ID and the second is you at the scene of the crime evidently using powers similar to your own to tear open a safe and rob a bank.  It appears you've been set up somehow...<br><br>You could show the people of Paragon City that this imposter clearly isn't you by investigating and clearing your name.<br><br>Alternatively you could confront Longbow for accusing you of something you're clearly not capable of doing."
// Answer Text :
"P2453747978" "HERO: Clear your name by investigating further."
// Answer Text :
"P2228836328" "VIGILANTE: Confront Longbow for wrongly accusing you."
// Page Rogue Text :
"P3592034245" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Wanted Poster With Your Face</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>While going about your business your gaze falls upon a Longbow wanted poster with your name and face on it.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>You pull the poster from its posted location and read it carefully</scale></color></font><br><br><color orange><scale 1.5>LONGBOW WANTED FUGITIVE</scale><br><br>ATTEMPTED MURDER, ARMED ROBBERY<br><br></color>Below this is a pair of pictures of you.  The first is a headshot of yourself used in your Paragon City hero ID and the second is you at the scene of the crime evidently using your powers to tear open a safe and rob a bank.  It appears you've been set up somehow...<br><br>Your villainous past is behind you, the last thing you need is the people of Paragon City doubting you now.  You could clear your name by investigating further.""
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


